comments.body: I think you are talking about Cksolo pool right? if so, then No, the last block that was found by cksolo was block # 733,739. The block you mentioned was found by "unknown" and that isn't cksolo for sure, here is a list that gets instantly updated when ckpool hits a block https://btc.com/stats/pool/Solo%20CKYou can use the same website to track other pools/blocks.

comments.author: DaveF
comments.body: It looks like that address just found another block. Could be an unknown pool or some new mining venture or really about a dozen other things.That in the end is the nice thing about BTC. It's cool to know who, but we don't NEED to know who.-Dave
